      "text": [
        "116 - وَقَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لِكُلِّ شَيْءٍ طَهُورٌ وَ طَهُورُ اَلْفَمِ اَلسِّوَاكُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.116 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Everything has a means of purification, and the means of purification for the mouth is the siwak (tooth cleaning).\""
        ]
      }
    }
